              role: 'user',
              content: `For this concept: "${masterConcept}"

Generate unlock questions for these 2 weakest principles:
1. ${lowestTwo[0].name} (scored ${lowestTwo[0].score}/10)
2. ${lowestTwo[1].name} (scored ${lowestTwo[1].score}/10)

Return JSON: {"questions": [{"principle": "${lowestTwo[0].principle}", "icon": "${lowestTwo[0].icon}", "name": "${lowestTwo[0].name}", "question": "sharp specific question"}, {"principle": "${lowestTwo[1].principle}", "icon": "${lowestTwo[1].icon}", "name": "${lowestTwo[1].name}", "question": "sharp specific question"}]}`
            }
